#!/bin/bash

windows=$(/opt/homebrew/bin/yabai -m query --windows --space)
dropover_exists=$(/opt/homebrew/bin/jq -r 'map(select(.app == "Dropover")) | length > 0' <<< "$windows")

if [ "$dropover_exists" = "true" ]; then
    echo "YES"
else
    echo "NO"
fi
